# CODEOWNERS — review routing for v2 document edits.
#
# Every PR opened by scripts/propose-edit.mjs (or the future chat-edit UI)
# touches a file under documents/<category>/, so we route reviewers per
# category. Replace the placeholder team handles below with real teams
# before turning on branch protection ("Require review from Code Owners").
#
# Match order matters in CODEOWNERS — first match wins. Keep the
# most-specific rules at the top and a final catch-all at the bottom.
#
# docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-policies/about-code-owners

# --- documents/ — per-category approvers ---------------------------------
documents/ISMS関連文書/      @afdpfrss/security-team
documents/人事考課/         @afdpfrss/hr-team
documents/年末調整/         @afdpfrss/hr-team
documents/労使協定/         @afdpfrss/hr-team
documents/各種規程・基準/   @afdpfrss/legal-team
documents/各種マニュアル/   @afdpfrss/ops-team
documents/設備運用ルール/   @afdpfrss/facilities-team
documents/発令/             @afdpfrss/hr-team
documents/会社案内/         @afdpfrss/comms-team
documents/その他業務ガイド/ @afdpfrss/ops-team

# --- code / config — engineering owns the platform itself ---------------
/lib/        @afdpfrss/eng
/app/        @afdpfrss/eng
/components/ @afdpfrss/eng
/scripts/    @afdpfrss/eng
/docs/       @afdpfrss/eng

# --- catch-all ----------------------------------------------------------
*            @afdpfrss/eng
